{"lemma":"صَيْدٌ","slug":"صَيْدٌ","root":"ص.#.د","root_slug":"ص-_-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-_-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"صَيْد","root":"صيد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25311"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D8%AF%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of صَادَ (ṣāda, “to hunt”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hunt, hunting, fishing"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"game (hunted wild animal)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"prey, booty"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Verbal noun of صَادَ (ṣāda, “to hunt”), from the root ص ي د (ṣ y d). Compare Hebrew ציד (tsáyid, “hunting”) and Classical Syriac ܨܝܕܐ (ṣayda, “hunting”)."},"ipa":["/sˤajd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25311","headword_ar":"صَيْدٌ","root":"Syd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an instance of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolN","text_ar":"فَعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or an inf. n. used as a subst. [properly so called, and therefore used in a sing. and in a pl. sense], (Msb, TA,) [i. e.] an inf. n. used in the place of the objective complement of its verb; (IJ, M;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Game, chase,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prey; an object,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"objects, of the chase"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maSiydN","text_ar":"مَصِيدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K, TA) used as a subst.; (TA;) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is taken, captured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caught;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought to be taken"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"captured"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caught;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the chase,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of a snare"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"trap,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by artifice of any kind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of wild animals"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of fowl &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of fish:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is repugnant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficult of approach,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shy, by nature, not to be taken but by means of artifice, whatever it be,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but lawful to be taken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no owner:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any wild animal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wild animals, whether, or not, taken"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought to be taken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, M:) but this last application of the word is a deviation from general usage: (M:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuyuwdN","text_ar":"صُيُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, Msb.) [Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quarry"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the hawk; the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prey"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any beast or bird &c.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayoduka","text_ar":"صَيْدُكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuHoramohu","text_ar":"لَا تُحْرَمْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd, A, but in the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sayodaka","text_ar":"صَيْدَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ailozamo Sayodaka","text_ar":"اِلْزَمْ صَيْدَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) is a prov. (Meyd, A) inciting one to seize an opportunity, (A,) applied to a man who seeks another to execute blood-revenge upon him, and lights upon him when he is inadvertent; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thy prey"},{"kind":"text","text":"has become within thy power, therefore"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be not thou neglectful of him"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so as to suffer him to escape, or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be not thou rendered hopeless of him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Meyd. [See also Freytag's Arab. Prov. i. 712; where"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHoramuhu","text_ar":"تُحْرَمُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuHoramohu","text_ar":"تُحْرَمْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SayadN","text_ar":"صَيَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","S","Mgh","K","L","IAar","M","Meyd","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}